audio_item.dc.abstract: [Program 75] : [Side 1] : [Part 1] : Tape 2 of 2; Wayne State Glee Club performs: Trosterin Musik; At the Round Earth's Imagined Corners; Salvation Belongeth To our God; Quatre Petite Prieres; Jubilate Deo Omnis Terra. Selections by The Four Muscatels: Haec Est Dies; I Dream of Jeannie; Deep River; Everytime I Feel the Spirit.
